                <div class="col-4 text-white">
                    <!-- Heading -->
                    <h1>
                        ID-Vault for organizations
                    </h1>

                    <!-- Text -->
                    <p>There are two main roles for organisations on the id-vault platform. The first and most common is varivier, a verivier is an organisation that uses user data for example for login purposes. The second roel is issuer, an organization that provides user data, for example the users phone number. In practice most issuers als also valiators.</p>

