                    </h2>

                    <!-- Text -->
                    <p>To use het id-vault user data you have to set up a user account and activate <a href="{{ path('app_documentation_glossary') }}#developers-portal">the developers portal</a> in that account. You can than add or join organisation and set up applications. Once you setup an application you can follow the simple <a href="{{ path('app_documentation_tutorial') }}">tutorial</a> to set up you id-vault login, or download one of our <a href="{{ path('app_documentation_tutorial') }}">plugins</a> for your framework or cms.</p>
                </div>
            </div> <!-- / .row -->
        </div> <!-- / .container -->
    </section>


